creator: NearOnes
descriptionHtml:
With NearOnes, people that need extra hands with tasks like groceries, cleaning, childcare, cooking, pet care, and deliveries, are connected with students willing to help.

Through the app, you can post a task in less than a minute, defining a time, location and budget. Students apply for it, you can choose to accept them, and everything is then dealt in a seamless way, including payments and reviews.

- Reliable
The students are screened for tasks like childcare and cleaning, to ensure safety and trust.

-Fast and convenient
You can get help with ad hoc, last-minute (<1 hour) needs. Payment goes easy and safe through the platform with iDeal or credit card.

- Insurance
The NearOnes’ Insurance through Aon insures users that work through this platform. It will make sure that you can have a peace of mind while students are performing tasks for you.*

-Young students
For young school students from 15 years and older, this is a fun and flexible way to make some extra money by helping others.

NearOnes is currently operating in Amsterdam and Amstelveen.

* visit www.nearones.nl for all terms.
descriptionShort: NearOnes -Get help with everyday tasks from reliable young students nearby

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
In this update we improved the following things to ensure an ever better experience:
- The chat shows a counter for unread messages
- On the map, we don't show full addresses anymore

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
In this release, we've made some fixes and you'll find a new feature to make the app even nicer to use, go on and try it!:)

title: NearOnes

creator: NearOnes
descriptionHtml:
With NearOnes, people that need extra hands with tasks like groceries, cleaning, childcare, cooking, pet care, and deliveries, are connected with reliable people that are willing to help. Save time for the things you love as a poster or earn money as a nearone.

Looking for help?

POST ANY TASK FOR FREE,
Make your needs heard - let the community know what task you need help with.

RECEIVE APPLICATIONS FROM SCREENED, PEER-REVIEWED PEOPLE,
Every nearone is screened for safety and security. Have peace of mind when accepting a nearone.

GET QUICK HELP,
Receive help with last-minute needs, even in the same hour. Over 6,000 nearones are ready to help in a thriving community.

& RELAX
In collaboration with AON, nearones are insured while performing tasks.*

Willing to help?

COMPLETE CHORES FOR NEIGHBOURS IN NEED,
Get things done!

WORK WHEN YOU WANT,
Browse through all posted tasks in one easy to use, interactive map. Choose which tasks to perform whenever you’re available.

& EARN MONEY
Payment is simple and easy - get paid quickly.

*visit www.nearones.nl for all terms.
descriptionShort: NearOnes -Get help with any daily task from reliable, vetted people nearby

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
With this new update, you'll be able to enjoy more things on the app and we solved some bugs! Among others:
- It's possible to edit your profile now
- The on-boarding became a lot easier and quicker

Have fun with NearOnes :)
